  still is not a real scope lock without one exact baseline cash-out and
  one same-currency gain threshold, and the resulting admission and novelty
  rules for Step-2 candidates. The same topic now also records that the
  dyadic coupled-flux ledger is exact only as an aggregation of the
  helical-triad core, and that the current honest bad-transfer target is a
  Tao-style shell-bridging packet pattern rather than a direct one-sided
